- Structure plan: Lead with the season's macro colour story, move into 9–10 priority shades with depth per shade (vibe, finish options, skin tone match), add a decision-making framework, close with nail prep for longevity.
- Tone direction: Confident colour editor — opinionated, specific, no hedging.

